{"tid":1843431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再有初步確診病人. 患者是香港人, 曾到訪武漢.","createTime":"2020-01-26T08:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T09:43:52.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e4d699a26e903b7d346bb0a97ef19ddda7b412","tid":1843431,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2550656/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2550656%2F&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGespe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=55502140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2550656/</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】消息指本港再新增高度懷疑個案 患者曾到訪武漢【不斷更新】<br />\n社會 15:02 2020/01/26 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，本港新增一宗高度懷疑武漢肺炎個案，患者來自武漢，首次的化驗對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，正進行更多化驗以確定，現在在律敦治醫院接受隔離治療。<strong>消息指患者在1月23日入院，是一名香港市民，曾到訪武漢。</strong><br />\n<br />\n本港至今已確診５宗武漢肺炎病例，患者全部來自武漢，現在在瑪嘉烈院傳染病中心接受隔離治療。政府昨日（25日）將本港的傳染病應變級別提升至最高級別緊急，同時取消未來多項的公眾活動，包括馬拉松，以及延長學校農曆年假至2月17日。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：伍瑋瑋"},{"pid":"efdbb6e04aae8f08c7932a37d194a5e03f900298","tid":1843431,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e58b4426fcfb0ac7dd695af116093585eeb59d3","tid":1843431,"uid":166996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"推 封關"},{"pid":"5625d4b692e02282652b499c22d252a444e52742","tid":1843431,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"水炮車？"},{"pid":"03c5a851d743bfa8d0c60e5c90a002c8e185d128","tid":1843431,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5625d4b692e02282652b499c22d252a444e52742","tid":1843431,"ui